<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="reunite-vt">reunite <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌriːjuː'naɪt/    美 /ˌriːjuː'naɪt/  </p>
<p>[常用于被动语态]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>再统一；再联合；重聚：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The children were finally <strong>reunited with</strong> their families. 
孩子们终于和自己的家人重聚了。</p></div></div>